{"pageProps":{"bookPath":"leetcode","postPath":"lc-unique-binary-search-trees-ii","post":{"title":"不同的二叉搜索树 II","body":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\">目录</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\">\n<li><a href=\"#_我的做法\">我的做法</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_官方题解\">官方题解</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"preamble\">\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>题目<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/unique-binary-search-trees-ii/\">95. 不同的二叉搜索树 II</a>。这一题比较简单，先说说沃动思路。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_我的做法\">我的做法</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>首先，当 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span> 时，答案是 <code>[]</code>；当 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span> 时，答案是 <code>[[1]]</code>；当 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n=2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span></span> 时，有对应以下 2 种 BST：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre>     2    1\n    /      \\\n   1        2</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>当 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n=3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span></span></span></span> 时，有对应以下 5 种 BST：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre>       3    2      3   1    1\n      /    / \\    /     \\    \\\n     2    1   3  1       3    2\n    /             \\     /      \\\n   1               2   2        3</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>观察一下上面两个图，我们似乎发现了规律：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 是树的最大节点，所以 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 要是是跟节点，要么是右子树的节点</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 是根节点时，其左子树是一个有 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n-1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span> 个节点的 BST</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 是右子树节点时，它不可能有右子树</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>更进一步地，如果 <code>t</code> 是一个拥有 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n-1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span> 个节点的子树，那么从 <code>t</code> 出发，根据上面的规律，我们可以得到一些有\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 个节点的子树。做法是这样的：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>把 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 作为新树的根节点，那么 <code>t</code> 就是新树的左子树</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>对 <code>t</code> 的最右侧节点依次做如下处理：</p>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>设 <code>r</code> 是 <code>t</code> 最右侧的某一个节点</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>把 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 作为 <code>r</code> 的右子节点，并把原来 <code>r</code> 的右子节点作为新节点的左子树</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这样，我们对所有的拥有 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n-1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span> 个节点的 BST 都做这样的处理，就可以得到所有拥有 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 个节点的 BST 了。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这里还有个麻烦的地方，就是答案要输出所有的子树，所以我们的代码里需要一端对树做深复制的逻辑。话不多说，代码如下：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-ts\" data-lang=\"ts\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 缓存所有已经算出来的具有 n 个节点的 BST</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> MAP: { [n: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>]: TreeNode[] } = {}\nMAP[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>] = []\nMAP[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] = [<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> TreeNode(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)]\n\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">generateTrees</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">n: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span></span>): <span class=\"hljs-title\">Array</span>&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">TreeNode</span> | <span class=\"hljs-title\">null</span>&gt; </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (!(n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> MAP)) generateTreesWithFromPrevious(n);\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> MAP[n];\n};\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 从所有 n-1 个节点的 BST 中生成所有 n 节点 BST</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">generateTreesWithFromPrevious</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">n: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span></span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (!((n - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> MAP)) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 如果 n-1 不在 MAP 里，就先生成</span>\n        generateTreesWithFromPrevious(n - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> trees = MAP[n - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>]\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> nTrees: TreeNode[] = []\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> tree of trees) {\n        generateTreesFromOnePrevious(tree, n, nTrees)\n    }\n    MAP[n] = nTrees;\n}\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 根据其中一个具有 n-1 个节点的 BST（参数 tree），产生 n 节点 BST，并把这些新 BST 放到 nTrees 数组里</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">generateTreesFromOnePrevious</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">tree: TreeNode, n: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>, nTrees: TreeNode[]</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// n 在顶部</span>\n    {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> [newTree] = copyTreeWithCutNode(tree, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n        nTrees.push(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> TreeNode(n, newTree))\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// n 在右侧</span>\n    {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> curr = tree; curr; curr = curr.right) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> cutValue = curr.val;\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> [newTree, cutNode] = copyTreeWithCutNode(tree, cutValue)\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> cutNodeRight = cutNode.right;\n            cutNode.right = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> TreeNode(n, cutNodeRight)\n            nTrees.push(newTree)\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 深复制一个树（参数 root），并记录割点</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 这里割点的意思是，被割掉右子树的节点，就是上面分析中说的 r</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">copyTreeWithCutNode</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">root: TreeNode, cutValue: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span></span>): [<span class=\"hljs-title\">TreeNode</span>, <span class=\"hljs-title\">TreeNode</span>] </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> newRoot: TreeNode = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> TreeNode(root.val)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cutNode: TreeNode = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>\n    copyOneLevel(newRoot, root, cutValue);\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> [newRoot, cutNode]\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">copyOneLevel</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">target: TreeNode, origin: TreeNode, cutValue: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span></span>) </span>{\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (target.val === cutValue) {\n            cutNode = target;\n        }\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (origin &amp;&amp; origin.left) {\n            target.left = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> TreeNode(origin.left.val)\n            copyOneLevel(target.left, origin.left, cutValue)\n        }\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (origin &amp;&amp; origin.right) {\n            target.right = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> TreeNode(origin.right.val)\n            copyOneLevel(target.right, origin.right, cutValue)\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>代码虽然很长，但是逻辑很简单，我第一遍写完有一个 bug，调一下就通过了。这段代码中，关于\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 的结果是从关于 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n-1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span> 的结果中得到的，所以这段代码形式上算是个 DP 吧。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>另外，上面的代码里 <code>TreeNode</code> 长这样：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-ts\" data-lang=\"ts\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> TreeNode {\n    val: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>\n    left: TreeNode | <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>\n    right: TreeNode | <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">constructor</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">val?: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>, left?: TreeNode | <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, right?: TreeNode | <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span></span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.val = (val===<span class=\"hljs-literal\">undefined</span> ? <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> : val)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.left = (left===<span class=\"hljs-literal\">undefined</span> ? <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span> : left)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.right = (right===<span class=\"hljs-literal\">undefined</span> ? <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span> : right)\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_官方题解\">官方题解</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>官方题解的思路更简单。BST 的根节点左子树节点值都小于根节点，右子树节点值都大于根节点，所以，只要使 1 到\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 中的每个数都做为根节点，然后（递归地）生成对应的所有左子树和右子树就好了。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-ts\" data-lang=\"ts\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">generateTrees</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">n: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span></span>): <span class=\"hljs-title\">Array</span>&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">TreeNode</span> | <span class=\"hljs-title\">null</span>&gt; </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (n === <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> []\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> generateTreesBetween(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, n);\n};\n\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">generateTreesBetween</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">start: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>, end: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span></span>): (<span class=\"hljs-params\">TreeNode|<span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span></span>)[] </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (start &gt; end) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> [<span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>]\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 逻辑上来说，返回 [] 会合适一些，但是返回 [null] 会使下面的 for 循环更容易处理</span>\n    }\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> result = []\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = start; i &lt;= end; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> leftTrees = generateTreesBetween(start, i - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>);\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> rightTrees = generateTreesBetween(i+<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, end);\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> j = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; j &lt; leftTrees.length; j++) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> k = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; k &lt; rightTrees.length; k++) {\n                result.push(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> TreeNode(i, leftTrees[j], rightTrees[k]))\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> result\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","createTime":1608912000000,"authorName":"weily","type":"adoc"},"book":{"title":"LeetCode","toc":[{"title":"53. 最大子数组","path":"lc-maximum-subarray"},{"title":"62. 不同路径","path":"lc-unique-paths"},{"title":"63. 不同路径 II","path":"lc-unique-paths-ii"},{"title":"64. 最小路径和","path":"lc-minimum-path-sum"},{"title":"70. 爬楼梯","path":"lc-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"95. 不同的二叉搜索树 II","path":"lc-unique-binary-search-trees-ii"},{"title":"96. 不同的二叉搜索树","path":"lc-unique-binary-search-trees"},{"title":"120. 三角形最小路径和","path":"lc-triangle"},{"title":"121. 买卖股票","path":"lc-buy-stock"},{"title":"132. 分割回文串 II","path":"lc-palindrome-partitioning-ii"},{"title":"198. 打家劫舍","path":"lc-house-robber"},{"title":"276. 栅栏涂色","path":"lc-paint-fence"},{"title":"303. 区域和检索 - 数组不可变","path":"lc-range-sum-query-immutable"},{"title":"746. 使用最小花费爬楼梯","path":"lc-min-cost-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"146. LRU 缓存机制","path":"lc-lru-cache"},{"title":"数完全二叉树节点","path":"lc-count-complete-tree-nodes"}],"path":"leetcode"}},"__N_SSG":true}